{
  "stem": "1975.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 199.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So many people don't know about that, but Berlin was actually liberated by a certain segment of the Russian Army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a very fierce battle because the young-- Berlin was surrounded by quite-- by-- quite a number, number of days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But who fought and who liberated Berlin were the, the, the troops that were-- that were actually [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] mostly prisoners, deserters, rapists, the, the worst of the troops.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They, they, they were assigned to the liberation of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were assigned specifically-- in order to-- for, I mean, to go to the first lines and go to the battle.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whoever survived would be commuted his sentence for-- I mean, he would be-- actually, he would be free and, and recognize his rights as a-- again.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was a-- it was a very fierce battle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it didn't really last too long because Hitler was already exhausted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he's-- had the young troops which were not ready to, to fight.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were too young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were-- had, like, 15-, 16-year-old boys who were-- who had a very bad training.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he held up until the last minute.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And incidentally, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that-- when we-- when Berlin was liberated, we came in right after-- afterwards.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And incidentally, I had also the privilege to be at the place where Hitler was, was, was burned, at the Reich Chancellery.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our regiment-- and our [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] regiment, actually, was, was the one that had-- was empowered to watch and to be at, at, at this specific, specific place.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I even met some, some American-- at a later date, some American soldiers-- an American, Sergeant [?",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
